Clay and Buck Sound Off H1 - The Best From This Week - Oct 23 2021


Biden hypocrisy on full display: Maskless at fancy dinner in Washington D.C. Even NBC's bland as they come Today Show fact-checks Fauci's fear that college football games would be COVID super-spreaders: 'Never happened.' Whatever became of double-masking? Lifetime politician, Biden screams at crowd: 'We have fewer Democracies in the world today than we did 15 years ago. Fewer. Not more, FEWER!' Twenty-two-year veteran of Washington state police forced to resign for refusing to follow state vaccine mandate. Delta Airlines CEO refuses to enforce Biden mandate.
